七海ひな(七海雛)之前已經用七瀬ひな(七瀨雛)的藝名闖出名號，不過那並不代表她不需要炒作，職棒圈應該也不會特別出來回應、這種片商宣傳慣用伎倆的手法，所以不如靜觀其變，說不定還會有更離譜的說法出現。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:19:41.000Z","msg":"一嚟咁重口味，條路好難行"},{"pid":"40a57260423f16f766dcb467a3aa903181b482fc","tid":2139242,"uid":252078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed21bcbe8856f293bc9afa1d03a30a5ae46f9e29","tid":2139242,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":68,"score":-66,"quote":{"pid":"e66d22b64b3f88b74c2e060e8ebd65799adf3992","tid":2139242,"uid":68944,"like":214,"dislike":5,"score":209,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:08:29.000Z","msg":"小弟今次真係J唔落手"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EZJUyQ8U0AAPUvi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEZJUyQ8U0AAPUvi.jpg&h=f59912f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:54:12.000Z","msg":"仲要假波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49c95cb28d7ce2917e4bd5117aaec1975c7da54","tid":2139242,"uid":252078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a7487b2265d8f4984dae1a65cc9d72778d8150f","tid":2139242,"uid":343268,"like":298,"dislike":0,"score":298,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:08:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:54:40.000Z","msg":"其實人地已經整左容<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d645722d2a0918fd8ed7079ef81e8e4416da14a","tid":2139242,"uid":50041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"40a57260423f16f766dcb467a3aa903181b482fc","tid":2139242,"uid":252078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed21bcbe8856f293bc9afa1d03a30a5ae46f9e29","tid":2139242,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":68,"score":-66,"quote":{"pid":"e66d22b64b3f88b74c2e060e8ebd65799adf3992","tid":2139242,"uid":68944,"like":214,"dislike":5,"score":209,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:08:29.000Z","msg":"小弟今次真係J唔落手"},"citedB